westerns.title: Westerns
westerns.description: Saddle up and explore the Wild West with these tales of outlaws, bandits, gunslingers and bounty hunters.

11453.title: Blindman
11453.description: A sightless gunslinger embarks on a bloody killing spree after Mexican banditos steal the precious cargo he was to deliver to Texas miners: 50 mail order brides!

274152.title: Gang of Roses II: Next Generation
274152.description: In 1874, a small crew of women have found the missing piece to a combination lock belonging to the U.S. Treasury, and decide to commit the a heist.

300461.title: Quigley Down Under
300461.description: A man hired as a sharpshooter travels to Australia, where he learns his new, high-paying job has a morbid catch that leaves him conflicted.

301924.title: Man of the West
301924.description: A reformed outlaw is left abandoned in a remote area after he intervenes in a train robbery, where he unexpectedly runs into his old gang.

301943.title: The Scalp Hunters
301943.description: A lively and ribald western about a frontier-wise fur trapper who loses his pelts to a band of Kiowas in exchange for a slave he doesn't want.

302157.title: Duel At Diablo
302157.description: A sweeping western tale about the conflict between the Apache and the white man as a cowboy travels with a family being pursued by the Apache.

302327.title: Guns Of The Magnificent Seven
302327.description: A noble gunfighter recruits a team of the deadliest cowboys in the West to help him free a peasant leader from a notorious Mexican prison.

302331.title: Return of the Magnificent Seven
302331.description: When a tyrant’s gunmen take all the men in a Mexican village hostage, several fighters must save the village and free its people from slave labor.

302681.title: The Alamo
302681.description: John Wayne and Richard Widmark star in this historical film spectacular about the attack by Mexican troops on the Alamo.

302696.title: Lawman
302696.description: Lee J. Cobb, Robert Duvall, Robert Ryan and Burt Lancaster star in this film that reveals a deadly and truthful look at the way the West really was.

303011.title: Geronimo
303011.description: Based on a true story, this historical saga follows a legendary Apache leader as he holds his ground against both U.S. and Mexican military forces.

303020.title: The White Buffalo
303020.description: Wild Bill Hickok and Crazy Horse, two legendary figures, head out on a quest for the demon albino buffalo in this haunting western tale.

303076.title: Chato's Land
303076.description: A half-white, half-Apache man dodges a vengeful posse after he kills a sheriff in self-defense. Both sides pay a heavy price in this Western.

304809.title: Support Your Local Gunfighter
304809.description: When a charming con man is mistaken for an infamous gunfighter, he decides to impersonate the gunfighter so he can earn money to pay his debts.

306921.title: Breakheart Pass
306921.description: Charles Bronson stars in this nerve-shattering mystery thriller about a treacherous train ride across the snowy western frontier.  Also stars Richard Crenna and Jill Ireland.

367634.title: 6 Guns
367634.description: A young woman enlists the aid of a bounty hunter so she can take revenge on the men who killed her husband and raped her.

378809.title: The Trail
378809.description: In 1848, Amelia joins a caravan headed west in pursuit of California gold. After a savage attack, she is left alone to battle hunger and the elements.

415240.title: Gallowwalkers
415240.description: A cursed gunman, whose victims come back from the dead, recruits a young warrior to help in the fight against a gang of zombies.

441464.title: The Proud Rebel
441464.description: A Confederate veteran living in the Yankee North struggles with his son's shock induced muteness and the hate of the Northerners.

448986.title: The Magnificent Seven Ride!
448986.description: After the murder of his wife, the leader of the original Seven recruits five tough convicts to help him rescue a group of women from vicious bandits.

451681.title: A Night in Old Mexico
451681.description: A financially strapped but proud elderly man and his estranged grandson find themselves targeted by drug dealers in search of a missing money bag.

451951.title: The Jade Pendant
451951.description: The Old West becomes a battleground for power and fortune as thousands of Chinese immigrants come to build railroads and two fall in love.

463179.title: Firetrail
463179.description: As the Union army storms through South Carolina, destroying everything in its path, a troubled Confederate captain is sent to the front lines.

463189.title: El Enamorado
463189.description: Ya había dejado las armas, pero por ayudar a una amiga y por su sed de justicia por la gente oprimida se convirtió en un héroe en el norte de México.

463196.title: Ahí Viene Martín Corona
463196.description: Todo el pueblo lo quiere por ser defensor de los pobres y desvalidos, pero tendrá que ganarse la confianza de una mujer a la que tiene que proteger.

463201.title: Juan Colorado
463201.description: El padre de Silvia quiere casarla con Rafael quien, por celos, quiere acabar con Juan. Silvia se viste de Juan para salvarle el pellejo.

466705.title: Wild Horses
466705.description: When a detective re-opens a 15-year-old cold case, he suspects that a boy who went missing was murdered, and that a local rancher was involved.

472570.title: Hellhounds of Alaska
472570.description: A fur-trapper battles the elements and robbers when a gold shipment is ambushed - leaving a boy in urgent need of medical attention.

480403.title: Warlock
480403.description: A famous gunman becomes the marshal of Warlock to end a gang's rampages, but is met with opposition by a former gang member-turned-deputy sheriff.

484812.title: A Bullet for the General
484812.description: Es la Revolución Mexicana, un extraño joven americano se une a una pandilla de traficantes de armas, pero el líder de los maleantes desconfía de él.

488136.title: Mahjong and the West
488136.description: Returning home to bury her mother, a young woman reunites with her childhood friend who forces her to confront a shared trauma from their past.

488455.title: My Name Is Nobody
488455.description: A young man attempts to convince his gunslinging idol to join him for a deadly showdown against the baddest, most dangerous men in the West.

488471.title: Kill or Be Killed
488471.description: In 1900, a vicious gang of cutthroat outlaws ride across Texas to recover a fortune in hidden loot in their most daring robbery yet.

488725.title: Hooded Angels
488725.description: Two female vigilantes on the run in the Civil War are chased by the law as an enforcer must choose between his love for one or bring her to justice.

491628.title: Far From Men
491628.description: A reclusive school teacher living in 1950s Algeria agrees to deliver a wanted man to a French court for trial, but helps him escape instead.

494263.title: The Confederate
494263.description: A young woman desperate to escape a dangerous arranged marriage disguises herself as a boy, joins the Confederate Cavalry, and falls for her captain.

494687.title: The John Wayne Story: The Early Years
494687.description: Witness the early life and career of John Wayne, one of the most famous actors in film history, as his rise to stardom was only just beginning.

495915.title: Stagecoach: The Texas Jack Story
495915.description: A thief's nefarious past catches up with him when a vengeful lawman refuses to leave the past alone, which forces them into a dangerous pursuit.

498106.title: Boots and Saddles
498106.description: When a prim English lord inherits a Western ranch, it’s up to Gene Autry and his sidekick to show him how to run the place like a real cowboy.

499215.title: A Man Called Horse
499215.description: In 1825, an aristocrat is captured by Sioux warriors. As he begins to understand them, he falls in love with a tribe member, and aspires to lead.

499716.title: Stagecoach
499716.description: Western classic that transcends the genre as a stagecoach carrying nine passengers through frontier wilderness faces an impending Apache attack.

499939.title: Godmonster of Indian Flats
499939.description: This creative horror film centers on an eight-foot-tall toxic sheep monster that terrorizes the wild west and destroys anything in its path.

507208.title: Guns of the Revolution
507208.description: War on the Church in Mexico hinges on one long-suffering Catholic priest's endurance after a crazed general outlaws religion with pillage and arrests.

511954.title: Rawhide Rangers
511954.description: Blackie's gang is creating havoc and the Ranger, Brand Calhoun and his brother go to investigate.

513129.title: The Riot Act
513129.description: At the turn of the century, a small town’s ghostly past is brought to light when a mysterious actress witnesses a murder at a revered opera house.

514356.title: Red River (Colorized)
514356.description: Colorized version of the Western classic about a desperate cattle drive over the famed Chisholm Trail as male rivals juggle revenge and determination.

516088.title: Hudson River Massacre
516088.description: In 19th Century Canada, a fur trapper leads a rebellion against a ruthless landowner by kidnapping his daughter and using her as a bartering tool.

516452.title: El Rodeo (Doblado)
516452.description: Una estrella de rodeo algo oxidada tiene que elegir entre cumplir una condena en la cárcel o enseñarle suertes vaqueras a una bola de chicos salvajes.

518180.title: Django (Dubbed)
518180.description: A mysterious loner who enters a ghost town on the US-Mexico border dragging a coffin behind him saves a prostitute and gets enmeshed in a savage feud.

530196.title: Eminence Hill
530196.description: Bent on vengeance, a notorious outlaw and his gang kill a couple of homesteaders and kidnap their daughter, as local religious fanatics battle back.

532335.title: Los Alegres Aguilares
532335.description: Un ricachón aventurero le ofrece dinero a un tipo idéntico a él para que se haga pasar por él con una señorita con la que no se quiere casar.

532336.title: Los Dos Rivales
532336.description: El heredero y la heredera de sus respectivos ranchos, con una rivalidad de años, se disfrazan del sexo opuesto para resolver sus problemas de dinero.

532639.title: El Gran McLintock (Doblado)
532639.description: Un magnate de la ganadería y la minería debe lidiar con su esposa que regresa a pedirle el divorcio, con su hija y con los problemas de su territorio.

535769.title: The Dead and the Damned
535769.description: When a meteor lands in a gold rush town in California, miners accidentally release its spores which then turns townsfolk into bloodthirsty monsters.

536862.title: The Big Trees (Restored & Uncut)
536862.description: A land baron battling a Quaker colony for control of giant sequoia trees finds sharks at his heels and forms an unlikely alliance.

540201.title: Ride Sweet Die Slow
540201.description: Following the tragic murder of their sister, a female band of gunslingers prepare to avenge her memory by taking down her killers.

541281.title: Brimstone
541281.description: When a vengeful preacher comes to town, a frontier family woman is wrongly accused of a crime and forced on the run into the unforgiving Wild West.

542231.title: Frank and Jesse
542231.description: The story of how Jesse and Frank James became robber outlaws after the South lost the Civil War and their youngest brother was murdered.

542782.title: Miracle at Sage Creek
542782.description: When tragedy strikes a frontier town in 1888 Wyoming, two long-feuding families finally come together to bury the hatchet just in time for Christmas.

544698.title: Wagons East!
544698.description: A group of settlers in the old west hire a drunken trail hand to guide them back to the east coast, but the journey is tougher than expected.

545172.title: Broken Arrow
545172.description: Western drama about a man trying to broker peace, with dramatic consequences, between settlers and Apaches in a time of tribal mistrust.

545181.title: The Laramie Kid
545181.description: Tom attempts to stop a bank robbery, but in the process is mistaken for one of the thieves. Now, his girlfriend Peggy must prove his innocence.

546230.title: Blue Montana Skies
546230.description: A cattleman’s mission to a northern outpost to catch fur smugglers becomes doubly interesting when he finds a dude ranch owned by a beautiful woman.

546234.title: Red River Valley
546234.description: Singing cowboy Autry helps Arizona cattlemen try to build a dam that will bring water to their parched lands, while businessmen plot their sabotage.

547102.title: Copper Bill
547102.description: Two Texas thieves take on the heist of their lives when they scheme to steal $80 million in hidden drug money from the ranch of a dead mob boss.

547137.title: Born to the Saddle
547137.description: When an earnest young man prepares for a horse race, he’s swept up in the plans of a fiendish gambler, who hopes to manipulate the contest.

547148.title: Billy the Kid in Santa Fe
547148.description: After escaping imprisonment for a crime he didn't commit, Billy joins allies Jeff and Fuzzy to seek some good, old-fashioned justice.

548633.title: Frontier Outlaws
548633.description: Minding his own business as a gold miner, Billy’s fortunes turn south when he’s framed for murder by outlaws bullying ranchers out of their land.

548726.title: Ghost Town
548726.description: After an elderly miner is attacked by outlaws and robbed, a brave cowboy attempts to save him, and gets blamed for the crime instead.

554593.title: The Proud and the Damned
554593.description: Five years after the end of the American Civil War, 5 ex-Confederate soldiers get caught up in a new civil war happening south of the U.S. border.

555086.title: The Duel
555086.description: A Texas ranger investigates a series of murders in a small town and uncovers a dark secret about the town’s charismatic leader.

555659.title: The Lone Avenger
555659.description: When a powerful banker suddenly commits suicide, his son, the lone-riding Cal Weston, smells foul play and sets out to find his father’s killer.

555897.title: Living by the Gun
555897.description: In this gruesome Western which questions the arduous road to redemption, a young woman must seek revenge against her estranged uncle.

555995.title: El Rostro Impenetrable (Doblado)
555995.description: Despues de robar un banco mexicano, papa Longworth toma el botin y deja a su socio Rio para ser capturado, pero Rio escapa y busca a papa en California.

556077.title: The Old Barn Dance
556077.description: A horse trader’s business and good name go belly up when a tractor company comes to town and its underhanded owner turns the residents against him.

556249.title: The Gambler Returns: The Luck of the Draw (Pt. 2)
556249.description: A legendary poker player meets legendary figures and encounters unscrupulous scoundrels while en route to participate in a lucrative card tournament.

558054.title: Toll of the Desert
558054.description: When his family is killed, a bitter cowboy becomes a ruthless hired gun, but unbeknownst to him, his son survived and is now the lawman on his trail.

562817.title: Susanna Pass
562817.description: A game warden does everything he can to stop a duo with evil intentions who plan to blow up a businessman’s lake to claim the oil beneath it.

562832.title: Twilight in the Sierras
562832.description: At a home for reformed ex-convicts, parole officer Roy uncovers a counterfeit currency operation while, himself, being falsely implicated in a murder.

562851.title: Young Bill Hickok
562851.description: At the close of the Civil War, a gold shipment is stolen by foreign agents planning to assassinate President Lincoln while the wrong man is blamed.

563905.title: Hickok
563905.description: Civil War veteran and infamous outlaw “Wild Bill” Hickok’s new life as a Kansas town marshal comes under threat by a nemesis with a deadly grudge.

565894.title: All Hat
565894.description: After Ray serves his sentence, he seeks to find a new start in the world of thoroughbred racing, where romance and trouble are always present.

579549.title: The Broken Star
579549.description: The more a deputy sheriff investigates the murder of a supposedly dangerous criminal, the more the answers point to someone he cares about deeply.

587116.title: Renegade
587116.description: A woman in a Gold Rush mine camp betrays her own heart by marrying a claim jumper instead of the gold miner she loves, with shattering results.

589218.title: Honor Among Thieves
589218.description: A civil war veteran travels back home to Texas only to learn that the situation there is worse than he ever imagined, as he enters a deadly duel.

592486.title: Lassie en Las Colinas Pintadas
592486.description: Following the murder of a successful gold prospector, his brave dog sets out to bring swift justice by putting away the heinous killer.

592714.title: Zane Grey: Under the Tonto Rim
592714.description: After a band of thieves robs his stagecoach, murders the driver, and kidnaps a passenger, Brad Canfield’s revenge plot lands him in jail.

594925.title: The Last Round-Up
594925.description: Gene Autry is a cattle rancher in the Old West trying to keep local ranchers and Native Americans from ruin by a tycoon out to steal their water.

594935.title: Twilight on the Rio Grande
594935.description: Gene Autry's investigation of the murder of his partner, leads him to Mexico, where he becomes involved with the beautiful singer whose father has also been killed, and finds a jewelry smuggling ring.

595009.title: Red Headed Stranger
595009.description: Fallen preacher Shay, who guns down his wife for her infidelity, is recruited by helpless sheriff Scoby to help him fight the villainous Clavers.

595456.title: Mule Train
595456.description: When natural cement is discovered by two prospectors, one is murdered during a claim jump attempt. Marshal Gene Autry befriends the lone prospector and tries to help him promote his cement discovery.

600587.title: Out of the Wild
600587.description: A down and out cowboy finds work training a troubled mustang, a horse whose past and temperament mirror his own. Based on the novel by Mark Rashid.

601252.title: McLintock!
601252.description: A cattle baron with the diplomatic savvy to keep peace between dueling power brokers in town can’t seem to get his wife and daughter under control.

605478.title: Valley of Fire
605478.description: The new mayor of a lawless town must get rid of its gambling king, import a group of gals to settle the men, and outgun a gang of rotten kidnappers.

606172.title: Masacre en El Convento
606172.description: Un grupo de criminales busca un tesoro en la apartada localidad donde hay un convento, pero las monjas se niegan a ofrecer información.

607215.title: Venganza Sangrienta (Doblado)
607215.description: Tom es un muchachillo de doce años quiere vengarse de los forajidos que asesinaron a sus padres y un buscador de oro sale en su ayuda.

607423.title: High Lonesome
607423.description: In Big Bend Country in Texas, a recent spate of unsolved murders get pinned on a mysterious young drifter in town who gets caught up with bad actors.

607630.title: Walden: Life in the Woods
607630.description: A fairytale of quiet desperation that re-imagines a Henry David Thoreau’s classic “Walden” as a radical and brooding Western fable.

608018.title: Fuerte Solitario (Doblado)
608018.description: En las áridas tierras fronterizas de Texas, hay una oleada de asesinatos y el mayor sospechoso es un joven vagabundo que se acaba de mudar.

609894.title: La Venganza De Los Cheyenes (Doblado)
609894.description: Cuando unos apaches secuestran a una joven pionera, su hermano se propone rescartarla y, para hallarla, pide ayuda a un prospector amigo de la bebida.

615524.title: Apache Country
615524.description: When a bad guy tries to control Native Americans by getting them drunk, cavalry scout Autry must break up a ring which uses raids to cover up crimes.

615528.title: Night Stage to Galveston
615528.description: Gene Autry and Pat Buttram work for a newspaper publisher, and find evidence of corruption in the Texas State Police.

615626.title: Más Valientes Que Los Hombres (Doblado)
615626.description: La aventura y drama de siete niños que pierden sus padres al cruzar el pais en un vagon con la esperanza de una vida mejor en el territorio de Oregon.

615627.title: El Ángel Y El Pistolero (Doblado)
615627.description: Quirt Evans, un chico malo en todos los aspectos, conoce a Penélope, una chica cuáquera y debe elegir entre su mundo y el mundo en el que vive ella.

616697.title: The Prodigal Cowboy
616697.description: Two brothers, Nick, an athletic high school football star, and Mark, a rising name on the rodeo circuit, have always been rivals but, after a family tragedy, the competition heats up for their father's attention in this Western-style, modern-day story of the prodigal son.

618560.title: Jesse James: Lawman
618560.description: Famed outlaw Jesse James finds himself on the other side of the law when a sheriff hires him to stop a criminal gang from taking over his small town.

620699.title: Outlaws: The Legend of O.B. Taggart
620699.description: Returning home after a long prison sentence, a former train robber finds himself battling his sons in his attempt to recover a stolen fortune in gold.

622109.title: En El Oeste Se Puede Hacer Amigo (Doblado)
622109.description: Un vivales huye por el Oeste de un pistolero que quiere que le cumpla a su hermana casándose y termina ayudándole a un chico a reclamar su herencia.

622110.title: It Can Be Done Amigo
622110.description: Two unlikely outlaws – one a fist-fighting drifter and the other a gunslinging pimp – help a child claim his inheritance without getting swindled.

622958.title: Outlaw's Buckle
622958.description: As a terrible storm rips through a small Texas town, a deranged serial killer, who is serving time, wreaks havoc inside the local prison.

623573.title: Haunting at Death Valley Junction
623573.description: The frightful Ghost of the Wild West comes to life once a year at a notorious hotel, and when summoned, haunts two paranormal investigator hosts.

624561.title: El Rebelde Orgulloso (Doblado)
624561.description: Un veterano confederado lidia con el odio de los norteños y con el mutismo de su hijo provocado por el trauma de la guerra civil de Estados Unidos.

625139.title: Blackwater
625139.description: In this seething Western tale, a raucous and deadly band of outlaws come to town and meet brave resistance from locals who aren’t having their spree.

627961.title: Big Muddy
627961.description: When a grifter’s son commits a crime, she must reconcile her own past sins and go on the run, hoping to avoid her revenge-seeking ex.

636072.title: Indians, Outlaws, Marshals and the Hangin' Judge
636072.description: Take a trip back to the Old West to hear about the most notorious judge, as described through his own words in his last known newspaper interview.

637938.title: Un Par A Todo Dar
637938.description: El terreno que les vendieron a Viruta y Capulina en Tepalcate de las Jarras, pueblo natal de Capulina, resultó ser un tétrico y espantoso chanchullo.

638331.title: Cowboys & Aliens
638331.description: “Iron Man” director Jon Favreau directed this sci-fi Western with Daniel Craig and Harrison Ford squaring off against a massive intergalactic threat.

638355.title: Debieron Ahorcarlos Antes
638355.description: Tres pillos intentan huir de la cárcel y recuperar el oro que uno de ellos le robó al ejército, pero no son los únicos que andan tras el preciado metal.

638471.title: El Hijo De Gabino Barrera
638471.description: El hijo del muerto Gabino Barrera quiere vengar a su padre y convoca a los campesinos para no vender los frutos de su trabajo a un par de acaparadores.

639140.title: Lauro Puñales
639140.description: Durante la usurpación huertista, un campesino se hace zapatista y se enamora de una viuda sin saber que la familia de ésta atentará contra su vida.

639262.title: La Captura De Gabino Barrera
639262.description: Gabino no quería meterse en broncas y menos en un país extranjero, pero lo seduce una mujer que ofrece llevarlo en su convertible a su rancho.

639529.title: Pistoleros Bajo El Sol
639529.description: Un hombre valiente llega a un pueblo sin ley, donde la gente vive aterrorizada, para dar con el canalla culpable de la muerte de su hermano.

641185.title: The Stranger Wore a Gun
641185.description: After the Civil War, a spy for the Confederacy absconds to Arizona to start a new life but gets reluctantly pulled into a stagecoach gold robbery.

642232.title: Four Faces West
642232.description: When a New Mexico cowpoke holds a banker at gunpoint to get an unsecured loan, offering an IOU, he must flee from the local marshal and his posse.

642235.title: Terror at Black Falls
642235.description: A Mexican gunslinger, unjustly imprisoned for trying to save his son from a lynch mob, is released and seeks revenge. But is his target the wrong man?

644009.title: Black Pioneer
644009.description: Based on the true story of an enslaved pioneer whose brave crosscountry journey to prepare the way for the Saints was vital to the settlement of Utah.

644877.title: Rio Lobo
644877.description: A former Union officer teams up with ex-Confederate rebels to find a traitor who caused the death of a close friend and now runs a lawless Texas town.

644879.title: Big Jake
644879.description: When his grandson is kidnapped, the feisty head of his estranged family goes home, supposedly to deliver the ransom, but intending to put up a fight.

645975.title: The Last Beyond
645975.description: A man whose entire world seems to be on the verge of slipping away during the Great Depression heads out for the wilds of Montana and a new life.

646736.title: They Call Me Trinity
646736.description: A bounty hunter and his outlaw brother become the goofy gunslinging duo standing in the way of a craven landowner’s plan to run out Mormon settlers.

646737.title: Trinity Is Still My Name
646737.description: In the process of honoring their father’s dying wish to become famous Old West outlaws, a pair of gunslinging brothers turn into do-gooders instead.

652105.title: Lone Rider (Español)
652105.description: Al regresar a su pueblo, un soldado descubre que el corrupto latifundista, mandamás del lugar, quiere adueñarse a las malas del negocio de su familia.

655703.title: Bass Reeves and the Brunter Brothers
655703.description: When a U.S. Deputy Marshal teams up with a lawman, they go on a radical adventure to track down the outlaw gang known as the Brunter brothers.

656779.title: Rifles Apache (Sub Esp)
656779.description: Comandante de un puesto avanzado de caballería de Arizona, odia a los apaches y los combate ferozmente

659798.title: Catch the Bullet
659798.description: A U.S. Marshal sets out to rescue his kidnapped son from a vengeful outlaw and his gang. Both parties face deadly dangers in the desert.

660658.title: Dead Men
660658.description: A young man and his estranged brother embark on a journey to avenge their father’s death, protect the Apache tribe, and reclaim their stolen land.

661180.title: Shootout at Osage Station
661180.description: This is the tale of Billy the Kid wannabe Caleb Bateman, an outlaw and notorious cattle rustler, and the shootout that led to his death.

663814.title: The Sisters Brothers
663814.description: Brothers and assassins Eli and Charlie Sisters pursue a prospector across the American Northwest in this witty reimagining of the cinematic Western.

664885.title: Stagecoach
664885.description: Seven desperate characters must pass through Geronimo country to get to Lordsburg. Their journey is fraught with danger, romance, and adventure.

666240.title: Everyday Miracles
666240.description: To escape his evangelist homelife, a reluctant faith healer finds refuge working as a ranch hand for a widower until his past catches up with him.

666804.title: Mackintosh and T.J.
666804.description: While passing through Dickens, Texas, Mackintosh’s car troubles lead him to spend time in town, where he meets T.J. The two soon become fast friends.

667509.title: Straight to Hell (Director's Cut)
667509.description: Four hapless bank robbers bury their loot and attempt to hide out in an abandoned desert town, but very soon find out that they are not alone.

667841.title: North of the Rio Grande
667841.description: When the brother of cowboy hero Hopalong Cassidy is murdered, he hatches a scheme to catch those responsible by posing as a wanted man.

670220.title: La Ley De La Fuerza (Doblado)
670220.description: Una colonia cuáquera intenta salvar a las secuoyas gigantes de un barón maderero que intenta cortarlas para hacer de ellas negocio.

671601.title: Band of Rebels
671601.description: A group of confederate soldiers uses their skills to travel behind enemy lines and take on deadly missions that reign havoc on the Union army.

671834.title: Heritage of the Desert
671834.description: When an engaged woman falls in love with a wounded man that her family is caring for, she flees her wedding and finds herself held hostage by outlaws.

676693.title: Galveston
676693.description: After escaping a trap and rescuing a sex worker in New Orleans, a hitman on borrowed time returns with her to his Texas hometown to plot his revenge.

676860.title: Bone Tomahawk
676860.description: When a group of individuals kidnaps settlers from a small town, an unlikely team of gunslingers, led by Sheriff Hunt, sets out to bring them home.

679467.title: Life Is Tough, Eh Providence?
679467.description: After capturing and freeing the same bandit to repeatedly collect the bounty, the eccentric Providence tries his luck with a wily local sheriff.

679540.title: Saga of Death Valley
679540.description: In 1895, 15 years after his father was gunned down in cold blood and his toddler brother was kidnapped, Roy sets out for revenge and a reunion.

680570.title: The Salvation
680570.description: Set in 1870s America, Jon Jensen, a European settler, unleashes a maelstrom of bloodshed in the Wild West. A white-knuckle tale of revenge.

680753.title: The Naked Hills
680753.description: A farmer in 1849 Indiana who catches a case of gold fever makes the cross-country trek to find the ‘mother lode’ hidden in the Californian hills.

681619.title: Joshua: The Black Rider
681619.description: When a soldier returns home from war, he discovers his mother has been murdered by a gang of men, forcing him to take matters into his own hands.

682033.title: The Englishman's Boy
682033.description: A powerful movie producer in 1920s Hollywood tries to track down an elusive Western star to offer the lead role in his upcoming motion picture.

682403.title: The Dude Bandit
682403.description: When a man's murder is made to look like a suicide, investigator Ace Cooper poses as a coward during the day but becomes Dude Bandit at night.

685621.title: The Ballad of Gregorio Cortez
685621.description: After he is accused of murdering a lawman in 1901 Texas, a Mexican-American farmer eludes a large posse for two weeks before he is finally captured.

689656.title: Outlaws and Angels
689656.description: When outlaws on the lam invade the home of an unsuspecting, seemingly innocent frontier family to hide out, a tense game of cat and mouse ensues.

693434.title: 30 Seconds in Hell
693434.description: The gunfighters of the OK Corral are brought back from the grave by the mysterious Destiny and her henchman Sorem to start the battle all over again.

694975.title: Quest for Clint
694975.description: Two Southern guys are forced to outmaneuver a series of nonstop criminal obstacles as they venture out West to meet their hero Clint Eastwood.

697756.title: Young Billy the Kid
697756.description: This film is an Old West comic book-style experience about William's myth, legend, and truth before he was known as Billy the Kid.

698761.title: Red Sun
698761.description: During an 1870 train heist, a gang steals a ceremonial Japanese sword meant as a gift for the U.S. President and prompts a manhunt for its recovery.

702674.title: El Caballo Bayo
702674.description: Un viejo villista es asesinado y su hijo Doroteo es auxiliado por Isabel quien lo hace su caporal y le obsequia un caballo con el que Doroteo corre.

702897.title: I Spit on Your Tombstone
702897.description: After six men viciously murder her family, a woman who was raised by the Comanche Indians sets off to bring the gang of ruthless killers to justice.

703975.title: Forsaken
703975.description: An embittered gunslinger attempts to make amends with his estranged reverend father while ruthless land-grabbers besiege their community.

705628.title: Shooting Star
705628.description: When Star's little sister is injured in a horse riding accident, she enters a shooting competition with a money prize that would cover her surgery.

707103.title: Blazing Saddles
707103.description: A corrupt governor will grant a reprieve to a convict under one condition: the condemned man agrees to serve as sheriff of a small Western town.

708985.title: Hell's Fury: Wanted Dead or Alive
708985.description: In a land where money-handlers control everything, a daughter must choose between taking care of her family and being truthful with the man she loves.

712235.title: Red River
712235.description: Matt and Tom, two cowmen, round up a ragtag bunch of cowboys and undergo a grueling cattle drive across a thousand miles of Texas landscape.

714654.title: Almost Heroes
714654.description: In 1804, a habitually drunk tracker and his foppish blowhard pal lead a crew of misfits on a race to beat Lewis and Clark to the Pacific Ocean.

715573.title: Buffalo Bill: Hero of the West
715573.description: In order to avoid an all-out war, Buffalo Bill finds himself looking to stop an illegal arms trade perpetuated by Big Sam Dolandson.

715585.title: Sartana Killed Them All
715585.description: Two ruthless outlaws are on the hunt for money missing from a robbery, and nothing will stop them until every last cent is in their hands.

723812.title: Black '47
723812.description: In 1847 western Ireland at the height of the Potato Famine, one soldier goes on a ruthless pursuit of justice against those who murdered his family.

723961.title: The Mystery of the Hooded Horsemen
723961.description: Tex becomes a victim of mistaken identity after he and his sidekick go up against a gang of masked riders terrorizing the owners of a gold mine.

100000629.title: Butch Cassidy and the Wild Bunch
100000629.description: When the infamous Butch Cassidy and his deadly band of outlaws pull off a high-dollar train robbery, the legendary Pinkertons raise a deadly posse to hunt them down.

100000695.title: A Reckoning
100000695.description: After her husband is brutally murdered, a widowed homesteader seeks revenge and leaves everything behind to hunt down his killer.

100000811.title: Night of the Tommyknockers
100000811.description: In Deer Creek, Nevada, as miners are blasting for gold, they accidentally release ancient monsters into the world, putting the whole town under siege.

100001167.title: The Wind
100001167.description: Forces of nature tremble with an unseen evil in this chilling tale of madness, paranoia and supernatural terror howling across the Western frontier.

100001226.title: El Camino Del Desierto (Doblado)
100001226.description: La historia de Samuel Mason, un héroe de la Guerra Revolucionaria, que recurre al crimen y forma una peligrosa banda de notorios bandidos.

100001279.title: High Noon Part II: The Return of Will Kane
100001279.description: Legendary Marshall Will Kane comes out of retirement to help free the town of Hadleyville from the iron grip of a tyrannical leader.

100001609.title: The Pleasant Valley War
100001609.description: The bloodiest family feud in American history, the Pleasant Valley War, led to more deaths than the O.K. Corral gunfight and the Hatfields vs. McCoys.

100001930.title: The Ranger, the Cook and a Hole in the Sky
100001930.description: In 1919, a cocky young ranger learns the ways of the wilderness from a grizzled veteran as they serve in the National Forest Service in Montana.

100002271.title: Cry Macho
100002271.description: A washed-up rodeo star is hired to retrieve his ex-boss’s troublesome son from Mexico. He bonds with the teen during their arduous trip to the border.

100002338.title: Joe Kidd
100002338.description: A gunslinger is hired by a wealthy land baron to stop the rebellion of local Mexican revolutionaries who claim they’ve been cheated out of their land.

100002340.title: High Plains Drifter
100002340.description: A gunslinging “Man with No Name” rides into the lawless Western settlement of Lago and makes a name for himself with a string of blazing battles.

100002695.title: Poker Alice
100002695.description: Disowned by her family because of her gambling habit, Alice wins a brothel in a game of poker and considers what life would be like as a madam.

100003063.title: Hacha De Guerra (Doblado)
100003063.description: Un artista que trabaja en el remoto Fort Alden se debate entre su amor por dos mujeres y la guerra entre los nativos americanos y los Estados Unidos.

0300006718.title: Sky King
0300006718.description: The story of a crime-fighting rancher who joins forces with his niece to board an airplane and stop dangerous criminals once and for all.

0300005346.title: The Son (Español)
0300005346.description: La lucha del "primer hijo de Texas" por establecerse como un poderoso ganadero y su posterior incursión en la naciente industria del petróleo.

0300006764.title: The Life and Legend of Wyatt Earp
0300006764.description: The battles and shoot-outs of Wyatt Earp, a Marshall in Kansas and then Arizona, who uses his guns and his trusty sidekicks to uphold the law.

0300005421.title: Tales of Wells Fargo
0300005421.description: For years, Jim Hardie has been a brave agent of Wells Fargo, always on the lookout for bad guys. Now, he just wants a quiet ranch life.

0300000081.title: Hell on Wheels
0300000081.description: An epic story of post-Civil War America, focusing on a Confederate soldier who sets out to exact revenge on the Union soldiers who killed his wife.

03753.title: The Cowboy Way
03753.description: Three modern-day cowboys living in Alabama work hard, play hard, and go about life at home with their families in this reality series.

0300008453.title: Bret Maverick
0300008453.description: James Garner returns to his original role of the slick pro poker player Bret Maverick as he settles into high adventure in the town of Sweetwater.

0300008430.title: How the West Was Won
0300008430.description: A Virginia-based family leaves their home to bravely travel across the country and make a new life in the wild, untamed American West.

0300008958.title: Bonanza
actors: Lorne Greene Pernell Roberts Dan Blocker Michael Landon Guy Williams
0300008958.description: On their 1,000-square mile Ponderosa Ranch in late-1850’s Nevada, Ben Cartwright and his three sons defend their land, business and fellow citizenry.

0300005112.title: The Rifleman
0300005112.description: A veteran of the American Civil War tends to his ranch when he isn't wielding his trusty rifle in an effort to help enforce the laws of the wild west.

0300005467.title: Dead Men: The TV Series
0300005467.description: After their father is murdered, two brothers attempt to get justice while also protecting the Apache tribe.

0300004736.title: Hopalong Cassidy
0300004736.description: Enjoy the classic gun-slinging Western adventures a well-meaning fellow and his loyal band of cowboys, who hail from the Bar 20 ranch.

0300009167.title: Wagon Train
0300009167.description: Follow the adventures of a wagon train as it travels through the plains, deserts, and mountains on its way from post-Civil War Missouri to California.
